<taxonomicName box="[375,518,366,391]" class="Aves" family="Thamnophilidae" genus="Myrmelastes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="18" pageNumber="487" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[375,518,366,391]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="487">Myrmelastes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by tail movements; habitat and foraging behavior differences are supportive.
</paragraph>
